---
title: Everything Bagel Tofu Tenders with Roasted Broccoli, Potato Wedges & Dipper Trio
description: Get ready to fry up crispy, savory tofu tenders, amped up with flavor from our everything bagel seasoning! You'll dip them in three types of sauces for ultimate treat: BBQ, ranch, and honey-Dijon. Roasted potato wedges and broccoli add even more depth to this inventive meal that’s sure to please everyone at the table.
